    "The study found that 46.86% of assessors preferred responses from physicians, 34.87% favored ChatGPT, and 18.27% favored ERNIE Bot.",
    "Physicians and ChatGPT showed higher accuracy and usefulness compared to ERNIE Bot, while ChatGPT outperformed both in empathy.",
